## 📂 Dataset

This dashboard was created using a sample HR dataset with fields such as:
- Employee ID
- Gender
- Department
- City
- Annual Salary
- Bonus
- Year of Recruitment
- Business Unit

> _You can modify or expand this dataset to fit your own use case._

---

## 🧠 Learnings

- Hands-on practice with DAX for calculations
- KPI creation and benchmarking
- Designing user-friendly, dynamic dashboards in Power BI
- Real-time filtering using slicers
